During my wanderings,

00:18:05.851 --> 00:18:06.810
I met a Taoist priest,

00:18:07.570 --> 00:18:09.931
an eminent scholar
from the Imperial Astronomical Bureau.

00:18:10.931 --> 00:18:11.851
Been through a lot,

00:18:12.290 --> 00:18:13.451
he brought me back here.

00:18:15.211 --> 00:18:16.330
Fate plays its tricks.

