00:19:33.171 --> 00:19:34.411
What matters now

00:19:35.371 --> 00:19:36.530
is to protect the Xue family.

00:19:39.851 --> 00:19:40.570
Rest assured.

00:19:42.131 --> 00:19:43.810
Lord Dingyuan saved my life once.

00:19:44.770 --> 00:19:46.891
I'll surely find a way
to protect his family.

00:19:48.730 --> 00:19:49.931
I need an imperial edict

00:19:50.651 --> 00:19:51.810
to legitimately

00:19:52.290 --> 00:19:53.691
meet with Lord Dingyuan.

00:19:57.980 --> 00:20:00.611
