You could break even
such an unbreakable item

00:20:36.530 --> 00:20:37.411
with mere sitting,

00:20:38.330 --> 00:20:40.891
proving you are so mighty

00:20:41.651 --> 00:20:43.570
that nothing can stop you

00:20:43.851 --> 00:20:45.171
in the war

00:20:45.651 --> 00:20:47.171
from now on.

00:20:47.651 --> 00:20:50.770
Long live Your Majesty!

