00:21:53.851 --> 00:21:55.090
You mean,

00:21:55.971 --> 00:21:57.371
the burden in my mind

00:21:58.570 --> 00:21:59.411
caused my sickness?

00:21:59.971 --> 00:22:00.611
Exactly.

00:22:02.211 --> 00:22:03.931
I deduced from the divination

00:22:04.611 --> 00:22:05.770
that the burden in your mind

00:22:06.131 --> 00:22:07.810
lies southeast,

00:22:08.010 --> 00:22:10.851
the mansion in the third street.

00:22:13.330 --> 00:22:14.451
It's the Xue Mansion.

